This merlot sauce is fantastic. I will definately make this dish again. I did notice when boiling/reducing the sauce a dark syrupy film developed on the side of my pot. I lowered the heat which seemed to help and also strained it when I finished reducing. I'm not sure if I was boiling at too high a heat or if it was the merlot. Neverless the resulting sauce was great!

